Cambewarra is located in New South Wales, Australia. It lies on the Kangaroo Valleyâ€“Nowra road, about 11 km northwest of Nowra and south of Cambewarra Mountain. At the , it had a population of 238. Cambewarra is a largely rural area, which surrounds Cambewarra Village.
